============================================================================

1.) Extract data_retriev folder and push that folder at experimental
    
    Eg:   scp /home/username/data_retrieve xxxx@202.164.53.122:~/public_html/

    Run script :- ""  sh script.sh ""

    FOR MANUAL PROCESS read " UserGuide.pdf "

